emperate Flux can't be multiquested, can it?)<br>
<br>
We tried the archaeologist's room, the preacher room and the king's chamber. The wizard finally popped in the king's chamber.<br>
<br>
Is there any particular site that's more likely to get wizards? I've got all the other piece of the staff in hand -- had a pretty good weekend, as far as accomplishing my questing goals goes -- and would like to free up my inventory space!<br>
<br>
Thanks. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ulordbug.showPublicProfile?language=EN>LordBug</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 68<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/16/01 12:26 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Heart of Ice (Rod of Temperate Flux)</span><hr size=1> I've found the King Room and Scryer Room best.  I got my heart from one in Preacher though.  I am told that the prison area is a good spot too, but I've never been there (no reason to <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ). <p><BR><BR>
